<span id="home">
  <section id="hero">
    <div id="shader"></div>
    <div id="wrapper">
      <div id="content">
        <div class="container">
          <p>Every Ticket Comes With Our Good Game Guarantee!</p>
          <div id="hero-search">
            <form id="form-home-search" name="formSearch" method="POST" action="/search">
              <input type="hidden" name="type" value="full" />
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="query" class="sr-only">Search Team, Stadium or City</label>
                <div class="input-group">
                  <input type="text" id="home-query" name="query" class="form-control" placeholder="Search by Team, Stadium or City..." />
                  <span class="input-group-btn">
                    <button class="btn btn-default" type="button" onclick="$('#form-home-search').submit();"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></button>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="press_images">
        <div class="mobile-images hidden-xs hidden-sm">
          <div class="spacing_div"><img src="<%= image_url "press2/Scout.png" %>"></div>
          <div class="spacing_div"><img src="<%= image_url "press/Crain's NY White.png" %>"></div>
          <div class="spacing_div"><img src="<%= image_url "press2/USA Today copy.png" %>"></div>
          <div class="spacing_div"><img src="<%= image_url "press2/CNBC copy.png" %>"></div>
          <div class="spacing_div"><img src="<%= image_url "press2/Sports Illustrated Red.png" %>"></div>
          <div class="spacing_div"><img src="<%= image_url "press2/Yahoo Finance.png" %>"></div>
          <div class="spacing_div"><img src="<%= image_url "press2/ESPN Radio copy.png" %>"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mobile-images hidden-md hidden-lg">
          <img src="<%= image_url "press2/Sports Illustrated Red.png" %>">
          <img src="<%= image_url "press2/USA Today copy.png" %>">
          <img src="<%= image_url "press/Crain's NY White.png" %>">
          <img src="<%= image_url "press2/CNBC copy.png" %>">
          <img src="<%= image_url "press2/Yahoo Finance.png" %>">  
          <img src="<%= image_url "press2/ESPN Radio copy.png" %>">
          <img src="<%= image_url "press2/MSN.png" %>">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <div id="results">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 hidden-xs hidden-sm">
            <h2 class="headerNew text-center">How Does the Good Game Guarantee Work?</h2>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="guarantee-item margin-divider-half">
                  <div class="img-holder" style="height: 100px;"><img src="<%= image_url "icon-tickets.png" %>" alt="Tickets"></div>
                  <p>Find your game &amp; purchase your tickets. Every ticket comes with our Good Game Guarantee at no additional cost!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="guarantee-item margin-divider-half">
                  <div class="img-holder" style="height: 100px;"><img src="<%= image_url "icon-stadium.png" %>" alt="Stadium"></div>
                  <p>If the home team loses by five or more runs you get 50% of the ticket price back.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="guarantee-item margin-divider-half">
                  <div class="img-holder" style="height: 100px;"><img src="<%= image_url "icon-handshake.png" %>" alt="Handshake"></div>
                  <p>Just come back to GameHedge to claim your refund!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="home-loading-data" class="row text-center" ng-if="loading != 5">
          <img src="<%= image_url "loadinfo.gif" %>">
        </div>
        <div class="row" ng-if="sports" ng-repeat="sport in sports">
          <h2 class="headerNew headerNew2" id="upcoming_title" ng-if="sport.near_events.length > 0">{{sport.name}} Upcoming Games Near You</h2>
            <div id="upcoming-games" class="row">
              <div class="col-md-3" ng-repeat="event in sport.near_events" style="height:180px">
                <div class="game-item">
                  <div class="date">{{event.occurs_at  | date:'EEEE, MMM dd'}}</div>
                  <div class="name margin-divider-half">
                    {{event.performances[0].performer.name}}<br />
                    <span>vs</span><br />
                    {{event.performances[1].performer.name}}
                  </div>
                  <div class="location margin-divider-half"><i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> <a href="/venue/{{event.venue.id}}/{{event.venue.slug}}">{{event.venue.name}}</a></div>
                  <div class="tickets margin-divider-half"><a href="/ticket/{{event.id}}">Buy Tickets</a></div>
                </div>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-12 hidden-md hidden-lg">
            <h2 class="headerNew text-center">How Does the Good Game Guarantee Work?</h2>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="guarantee-item margin-divider-half">
                  <div class="img-holder"><img src="<%= image_url "icon-tickets.png" %>" alt="Tickets"></div>
                  <p>Find your game &amp; purchase your tickets. Every ticket comes with our Good Game Guarantee at no additional cost!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="guarantee-item margin-divider-half">
                  <div class="img-holder"><img src="<%= image_url "icon-stadium.png" %>" alt="Stadium"></div>
                  <p>If the home team loses by five or more runs you get 50% of the ticket price back.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="guarantee-item margin-divider-half">
                  <div class="img-holder"><img src="<%= image_url "icon-handshake.png" %>" alt="Handshake"></div>
                  <p>Just come back to GameHedge.com for your refund!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section id="home-why">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4"><img src="<%= image_url "icon-fans.png" %>" alt="Fans" /></div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <h2>The GameHedge Story</h2>
            <p>We are fans like you.</p>
            <p>We invest our time, our passion and our cash supporting our teams. Sometimes things are amazing! Our favorite hitter launches a walk-off rocket to the upper deck; our QB throws a TD to the back of the end zone with 12 ticks left; or our rookie sharp-shooter hits a fade away 3 at the buzzer. Woo hoo!!</p>
            <p>But ... sometimes the team just doesn't return the love. You spend $400 on tix for the family, fight traffic for 3 hours and then ... well it's 6-0 in the fourth and your ace flame thrower heads to the showers with a tweaked hammie. If you're a true fan, you've been there.</p>
            <p>That's why we created GameHedge.</p>
            <p>When you bleed for your team ... GameHedge has a Band-Aid.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4"><img src="<%= image_url "badge-gamehedge.png" %>" alt="GameHedge" /></div>
          <div class="col-md-8"><button style="font-size: 20px;text-transform: uppercase;text-decoration: none;" class="button green" onclick="window.location.href = '/faq'">Still Have Questions?</button></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</span>